        <a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/03-standards/schemas/src/schemas/v3/pdtf-transaction.json" title="source/03-standards/schemas/src/schemas/v3/pdtf-transaction.json"><code>pdtf-transaction.json</code></a> schema, plus stackable overlays for each
        UK industry form. Overlays merge into the base via custom deep-merge logic.
      </p>

