          merge semantics, validator patterns.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/03-standards/trust-framework/CLAUDE.md"><code>source/03-standards/trust-framework/CLAUDE.md</code></a> — the Trust
          Framework spec, governance, examples, Mintlify docs.
        </li>
        <li>
          <code>source/03-standards/trust-framework/docs/Draft_ Property Data Trust Framework 2 Specification.md</code>
          — the formal spec being prepared for v2.0.
        </li>
      </ol>

